      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory paint, retaining a deep, lustrous shine. While there are a few minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and one small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper, the body is straight and free of any major dents. Inside, you\u2019ll find a clean, smoke-free cabin. The premium upholstery is in great shape, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and premium audio system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs whisper-quiet. I have followed a rigorous maintenance schedule, with a comprehensive service history included; the most recent visit included a fresh oil change, new cabin filters, and a brake fluid flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, ensuring you won't need an upgrade anytime soon. This car drives tight and true, offering a smooth, confident experience on both city streets and highways.",
